text: This is one of my all-time favorite movies.  Iâ€™ve watched more than 10 times and every single time, it brings me to tears and fills me with hope.  I love that this is based on a true story, reminding us of the timeless Truth that the gospel of Jesus Christ is our only hope.  This is a movie to watch and share with others.  As we watch people transform and move from hatred/fear/division to genuine healing/peace/unity, it helps us to see that the answer is found only in the gospel.  It reminds us that GOD has not changed, HE IS WHO HE SAYS HE IS.  The gospel reminds us that every human being matters to GOD and HE has made a way for us to know HIM, and to truly love one another.  Great movie, great story, great acting.  Find hope in these troubled times and know that every soul matters to GOD.
author: Maria Nelson
